Running ILIAS3 requires PHP 4.3.0 and the PEAR packages 'Auth' and 'HTML' which
are contained in this archive.

Installation
------------

Locate your PEAR directory (e.g. /opt/ilias/php/lib/php) and extract the contents
of pear_ilias3.tar.gz into this directory.

Getting PEAR via CVS
--------------------

The latest development version of each PEAR module may be obtained from the PEAR
CVS repository:

cvs -d :pserver:cvsread@cvs.php.net:/repository login
Passwort: phpfi

cvs -d :pserver:cvsread@cvs.php.net:/repository co pear/Auth

Instead of 'Auth' you may use any valid module name. If you only enter 'co pear'
you will get all modules at once (~9 MB) 
